						               													<description>Sci-Fi Trivia is a game for any number of players.  Players take turns rolling a die to select one of six science fiction trivia categories and then attempt to answer a question on that subject.  If they answer correctly, the player scores one point and rolls for another category.  If the answer is incorrect, play passes passed to the next player who rolls to select a new category.  If a player gets six consecutive questions correct, they score a bonus two points.  The game ends when a player has scored points for every category and the player with the highest score wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;From the box:&amp;#10;Sci-Fi Trivia - a game for sci-fi buffs aged teen and up - complete on its own or a great add-on to other trivia games.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;2,400 questions and answers on popular sci-fi subjects including: The Golden Age, Multi Media, New Wave, Cult Movies, Cult T.V. and The Classics.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Ideal for home and compact enough for travel, a complete trivia game on its own or a great add-on to other trivia games.  Sci-Fi trivia will entertain, stimulate and challenge your mental faculties.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
